            "title": "欧洲股市早段下跌\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段下跌。英国富时100指数报8,836.04点，跌48.88点(0.55%)；德国DAX指数报23,457.42点，跌314.03点(1.32%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,674.33点，跌90.78点(1.17%)。 <br/> (WL)</span>\n</div>",
